ccnd:
	This directory includes the csrc/ccnd code and has everything
	needed to run ccnd.  We provide an Android logging function.

openssl:
	ccnd needs libcrypto.  This is based on the Android port.

controller:
	This is the JNI interface and statically binds everything
	in to one shared object file.

